law.history: Repealed 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 139, sec. 11. -- Amended 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 202, sec. 13. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 204, sec. 6.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Payments by counties to Division of Forestry; computation; crediting and use; liability of county; settlement of disputes as to acreage.
